Detailed Description

This packet should be the only searchpacket needed for now.

(Overview/User/Proxy-search should be possible to do). Currently user-search is supported.

Member Enumeration Documentation

enum SearchRequestPacket::search_t
 

Enumeration values:
USER_SEARCH  Same as old UserSearchRequestPacket.
OVERVIEW_SEARCH  Search for cities etc. (on overview maps).
PROXIMITY_SEARCH  Means that the items in allowedRegions should be expanded to matches.
